Visit Luanda will make it easier than ever to find the most worthy places to visit. You can scroll through the carefully selected highlights of the city, choose where to sleep and where to eat, plan and view your walking or driving circuit around the city and much more:

- Locate the highlights of the city on the map a check how far they are from you;
- Flip through the photos to see additional details;
- Save your favorite places in a convenient way to check them again later;
- Directly access their phone number and other details as working hours, website, e-mail address, etc;
- See reviews to help you decide wether it's worth your visit;
- Ask for a route and plan your visit by walking or driving;
- Can't find a place you have heard of? No problem! Just use the fast search buttons or the text search to find dozens of additional places.

